    "author_association": "COLLABORATOR",
    "body": "The Engine WG reviewed this issue yesterday and believe this to be an issue with `Windows Terminal` - see https://github.com/microsoft/terminal/issues/8000. If that turns out not to be the case, we'll update this issue. \r\n\r\nNo one could reproduce this issue in other terminals e.g iTerm and Ubuntu 20.04 terminal e.g.:\r\n\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/5177512/131932279-fd52f155-0198-4a97-9099-cd20336fcc6e.png)\r\n\r\nBut we could repro the issue running Bash in WSL in Windows Terminal (no PowerShell involved):\r\n\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/5177512/131932366-c56745ca-2a35-4f8b-bbda-1d9e012104e7.png)\r\n",
